metadata.name: "We Are One"
metadata.description:
"We Are One"

Each one of us have the power to live harmoniously with one another on this earth. We have one life to live here and we have to make the most of it. Remind yourself that you have the power in your hands and in your mind to make this life here on earth worth living up to your fullest potential.

ChrisParam x PatrickLawler x St4rfox

This is the first NFT we artists have collaborated on and is an exclusive 1/1. We hope you enjoy our creation!

We are sending an exclusive physical Infinite Objects 7" LCD screen on a custom wooden stand with purchase!

"Live to Inspire"
